{"tid":2121669,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"穆迪：全球航空客運需求2023年底才重返疫情前水平","createTime":"2020-07-23T12:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T08:57:10.000Z","uid":225931,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7eee260b57cf1e76206aa68e9a3ad63b896a6784","tid":2121669,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2698823/202_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2698823%2F202_1024.png&h=1c4285c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評級機構穆迪報告指，即使研發出有效疫苗及藥物，全球航空客運需求要到2023年底才能夠恢復至疫情前水平。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，航空公司及機場將大致同步恢復，隨著航空公司恢復航班，飛機租賃公司才會復蘇。至於波音及空中巴士等飛機製造商，將會是整個航空業最後恢復一環。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪說，近期新型肺炎確診個案上升，<span class=\"red\">若各國政府收緊社交距離等防疫措施，航空業復蘇步伐將會更慢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n報告又提到，疫情爆發後，全球航空旅行需求在數星期內急挫超過90%，而航空客運去年對全球經濟總值貢獻約3%，航空業衰退大幅影響全球經濟。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0283c43fa695414f22dad57905b3f2c5dc3dd3d5","tid":2121669,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f97bd299000191c240252e2b11294a76b0fc891","tid":2121669,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b05501259cb73204aa4e2de659fd459dad7f8a2","tid":2121669,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:54:45.000Z","msg":"武肺嘅極限已經到左"},{"pid":"0835b9b2120f10b1d759e0058528c929890acd59","tid":2121669,"uid":39312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"咁樂觀呀？"}]}